'''Geograph Channel Islands''' is a [[Web application|web-based]] project, initiated in April 2010,<ref>[http://www.geograph.org.gg/photo/1 First image uploaded]</ref> to create a freely accessible archive of geographically located photographs of the Channel Islands.<ref>[http://www.geograph.org.gg/ Official website]</ref> Photographs in the Geograph Channel Islands collection are chosen to illustrate geographical features all parts of the Channel Islands. It is an offshoot of [[Geograph Britain and Ireland]] which began in March 2008.<ref>[https://www.geograph.org.uk/ UK and RoI site]</ref>
